      "text": "（アメリカに来るなり、スリクスは解散すると）\n（言われてしまったが……一体、何があったんだ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（アメリカに来るなり、スリクスは解散すると）\n（言われてしまったが……一体、何があったんだ！？）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.58609972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんとmihoさんは何も話してくれないし）\n（唯一、どうにか事情を聞けそうだったのが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（kanaさんとmihoさんは何も話してくれないし）\n（唯一、どうにか事情を聞けそうだったのが……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7696598053,
      "endTime": 13.642857170100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.8264172554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あー、あの二人、今凄く荒れてるんで\n下手に突っつかない方がいいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あー、あの二人、今凄く荒れてるんで\n下手に突っつかない方がいいですよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8264172554,
      "endTime": 20.142857170099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "賃貸の壁を蹴らない程度の理性はギリ残ってますけど\n帰国までスーツケースが無事だといいんですけどねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "賃貸の壁を蹴らない程度の理性はギリ残ってますけど\n帰国までスーツケースが無事だといいんですけどねー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3264172554,
      "endTime": 29.400385952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.5930839221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……kanaさん、そんなに暴れてるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あの……kanaさん、そんなに暴れてるんですか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5930839221,
      "endTime": 33.6669615428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaとは言ってませんけど、まぁ合ってます\nったく、物に八つ当たりするなっての、あのガキ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kanaとは言ってませんけど、まぁ合ってます\nったく、物に八つ当たりするなっての、あのガキ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8505216281,
      "endTime": 42.4838546435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6838549614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの……解散を考え直してもらうことは出来ませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あの……解散を考え直してもらうことは出来ませんか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6838549614,
      "endTime": 47.1534692764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺はスリクスの迫力あるステージが好きでしたし\nきっとファンの人達も、そうだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "俺はスリクスの迫力あるステージが好きでしたし\nきっとファンの人達も、そうだと思うんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3370293617,
      "endTime": 52.917029571499995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1005896568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "無理無理。解散はもう決定事項ですから\nま、そんなことはひとまず置いておいて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "無理無理。解散はもう決定事項ですから\nま、そんなことはひとまず置いておいて",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1005896568,
      "endTime": 60.0886623382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3005896568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私の大事な大事な打ち合わせなんですから\n{user}さんも、よろしく頼みますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日は私の大事な大事な打ち合わせなんですから\n{user}さんも、よろしく頼みますよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3005896568,
      "endTime": 66.8175510406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0339229901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ラムジーさんは、ショービジネス会社の社長で\nこの方面の若手への出資を積極的にやってる人です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ラムジーさんは、ショービジネス会社の社長で\nこの方面の若手への出資を積極的にやってる人です",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0339229901,
      "endTime": 74.5912247975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな大物を味方に出来れば、もう大成功間違いなし！\nふふ、ここから私の人生の第二幕が始まるのよ……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そんな大物を味方に出来れば、もう大成功間違いなし！\nふふ、ここから私の人生の第二幕が始まるのよ……！！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8005896568,
      "endTime": 84.8328122138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6667009353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
